query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS proposals (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  createdByUserId INT NOT NULL,
  dataMesAno VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  empresa VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  cnpj VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL,
  endereco TEXT NOT NULL,
  dataApresentacao VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  valorCaptacao INT NOT NULL,
  nomeProjeto VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  lastroAtivo VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  visaoGeral TEXT NOT NULL,
  captacaoInicial TEXT NOT NULL,
  destinacaoRecursos TEXT NOT NULL,
  prazoExecucao VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  prazoCaptacao VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  valorFixoInicial INT NOT NULL,
  taxaSucesso INT NOT NULL,
  valorLiquidoTotal INT NOT NULL,
  pdfUrl TEXT,
  pdfKey VARCHAR(255),
  status ENUM('rascunho', 'gerado', 'enviado') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'rascunho',
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  updatedAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  INDEX created_by_idx (createdByUserId),
  INDEX status_idx (status)
);
